{
  "stem": "1873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he did give me a blanket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I sold the blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bought a little gun from a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pele was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bought it with a blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to hide this pistol where the-- you know, in the old tanneries, there weren't electrical motors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a horse, which was-- his face-- his eyes were tied.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did run, day and night, all around, turning the-- the engine, the-- the-- the-- or wheels, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and there was a haystack, for-- for food for this horse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I hide it in the haystack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April 28, while sleeping, I hear a rifle shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I understood that something terrible happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I look out the window, through the attic, and I see the soldiers, Nazi soldiers, Ukrainians coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They smashed the gate from the tannery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But most of us were hidden already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had special hiding places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As I mentioned, Izbica was in a valley.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All around were hills.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so the-- the tannery was built in on one side of the hill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we took out a panel and digged a big place in the hill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later, the panel was so very nicely closed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so-- and they looked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left, the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't find us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could hear every word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, we heard voices in Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They must be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have seen them yesterday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't escape.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're hiding something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They must be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans did come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally, I remember, they were pulling the panels out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, when they were pulling the panel, light did come in into our hiding place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were flashing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The light was flashing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
